grade_preconditions.en:
To obtain a "pass" grade for the course, students must:
Complete all assignments successfully (quizzes, individual homework, group work);
AND participate in at least 60% (6 out of 10) of lectures;
AND participate in the seminar where their group presents the results of the group work;
AND participate in the seminar dedicated to retrospective for the group work.

