results_available_from.en:
Assessment results for the quizzes are generated automatically when the students submit their answers for the quizzes;
Assessment results for the individual homework will be announced between 17-MAR-2025 and 7-APR-2025.
Assessment results for the group work will be announced between 6-MAY-2025 and 21-MAY-2025.

